&lt;p&gt;   Whenever the consumer coordinator sends a response that doesn&apos;t match the client consumer subscription, ignore the assignment and rejoin the group.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   Testing strategy: create a mocked client that first sends an assignment response that doesn&apos;t match the client subscription followed by an assignment response that does match the client subscription.&lt;/p&gt;

